Commit Message:
Initial commit

Copy of latest sigal galleria theme

Remove Map support

Remove Leafet scripts/images/style
Configure galleria preferences
Remove Google/Piwik/CDN stuff
Show first image when pressing up key, remove map key
Remove more map related things

Use 2 space indent

Do not close br tag.
Update styling and footer.
Disable thumbnails carousel animation.
Remove alternate styles for wide screens.
Reduce space beween thumbnails.
Improve scaling
More menu to included template
Menu styling.
Image height/width fine tuning.
Remove unused parts.
Add license
Wrap photo below menu on mobile.
Remove text shadows.
Reduce footer font size.
Use vh units to limit max-height for the gallery.
Rename LICENSE.md to LICENSE
Show full gallery menu for each album
Reduce side margins.
Move author info to the menu
Reduce space between thumbnails.
Reduce menu font size.
Use light background and dark text colors.

Reset galleria css to original included in sigal.
Put overwrites in style.css
Update to Galleria v1.5.6
Update thumbnail borders and opacity and active image highlighting.

Set thumbnail background to black to preserve expected effect from opacity.
Set bottom border to white to blend with background.
Otherwise the black background will appear as the border.

Use white background for the galleria container,
Keeps white background on fullscreen.
Replace fullscreen icon by SVG.
Remove unused icons.
Make Galleria image map icons black.

Only show subalbums for the current ancestors in the menu.
And highlight the current active album.
Add background to fullscreen button for contrast.
Combine CSS rules and remove background on hover thumbnail navigation.
Invert colors for the loader spinner.
Fix logic for showing submenus at higher depths.

Update menu style.
Fix submenu indentation.
Reduce font-size, fixed line-height, normal font-variant.

Place author link above the menu.
Prevents flashing in menu while gallery is loading.
Use larger font-size in menu on touch devices.
Each CSS selector on a new line.
Remove prints from full_menu plugin.
Reorder some CSS styles.
Remove unused CSS styles.

Show less of the menu on touch devices, show only:
- siblings of the current album
- direct children of the current album
- ancestors of the current album
Make controls and thumbnail container same height as thumbnails.
Add padding around images when no JS is available.
Ensure the thumbnails have the same height.
Update jQuery to 3.2.1

Use animated SVG instead of GIF for the loader indicator.
Place it in the center of the image stage.
Set image name and datetime in alt, do not use title.
Remove config already set by classic theme.
Create LICENSE
Update README.md

Make the full_menu plugin an installable Python package.
Convert README to rst.
Move static and template files into the package.
Add theme templates and static as package_data.

Add plugin to set the theme to this theme.
Puts the absolute path to the theme/package dir in the theme settings.
Add demo gallery.
Add travis CI to check if demo builds correctly.
Not using Font Awesome icons.
Add installation instructions and shields to README
Improve CSS selectors to fix style when using full screen in an iframe.
Add comment about theme configuration.
Add some blank lines in CSS.
Fix no-js styling.

Do not render author

if no author is given. If author_link is set in settings use it. If author_link is not set, make author link to root album.
Add editorconfig.
Use elif instead of separate if statement for exclusive options.
Fix indent for script in script tag.

Remove copyright/license and encoding from plugin files.
See LICENSE file for license info.
UTF-8 is default for Python 3.
Add sorting limitation to full_menu docstring.

Update normalize to v7.
Use normalize in template.

Add gallery title setting, make this link to root.
The author_link is currently not used.
Author is used in metadata.
Add deployment of the demo site to gh-pages.
Add link to demo page in README.

Move setup configuration to setup.cfg.
Update pip install command in readme.
Add make commands to clean and build dist files.
Add dist and build files to gitignore.
Change default fonts

Use gallery title as page title.
Only add subalbum titles if they dont match name of source directory.
Fix path to normalize.css
Prevent global scrollbar, only menu should need a scrollbar.
Prevent wrapping long album names.
Rename templates for compatibility with latest sigal.
Add GitHub actions to replace travis CI
Add deploy to gh-pages
Fix link in readme to actions
Add more testing requirements
Update demo build configuration

Use specific action for checking html5 output

No longer required to install Open JDK.
Remove validate extras require.
Fix isort error
Configure flake8/isort
Less newlines in githubactions
Fix isort error
Add information on alternative way of setting the theme
Add movie example to demo
Install ffmpeg when creating demo
Remove badges

Add content-side of iframe resizer

Inform parent of size and changes to size.
Change date format for images
Update workflow
Dictionaries are already ordered
Breadcrumbs contain titles, not names
Skip date if not available
Always load iframe resizer
Update line heights for menu
Support dark-mode
Make controls more visible in dark mode
Fix editorconfig selector
Fix menu showing below gallery when full screen
Invert some more icons to be visible in dark mode
Use jQuery 3.5.1

Rework some margins

Remove margin on body, add margins (spacing) on menu and gallery.
Update used actions and rename step names
Update Makefile, setup.cfg, .editorconfig, and actions
Replace http by https in demo
Add a few more spaced between file name and date time
Enable showing info below photos

Bump version

Update links to https.
Rename workflows

Convert README to markdown

Add shields to README.
Update Media properties used in template for new sigal version

Remove leaflet static files included by default by sigal

Leaflet is not used by this theme, those static files are unnecessary.
Remove max-height
Add dependabot config
